OL,7,FA surgeon who carried out hundreds of
OL,8,F"unnecessary" mesh operations has
OL,9,Fapologised to his patients after being
OL,10,Fsuspended.
OL,12,FA tribunal has today (18 July) ruled
OL,13,Fthat Antony Dixon failed to provide
OL,14,Fadequate clinical care and ruled he
OL,15,Fcannot practice medicine for six
OL,16,Fmonths.
