OL,3,CSurgeon who carried out hundreds of
OL,4,C'unnecessary' mesh operations is
OL,5,Csuspended
OL,7,FMr Dixon pioneered a controversial
OL,8,Ftype of mesh surgery. Hundreds of his
OL,9,Fpatients have previously come forward
OL,10,Fto claim they suffered agonising side
OL,11,Feffects after he operated on them at
OL,12,FSpire Hospital Bristol and Southmead
OL,13,FHospital, also in Bristol.
OL,15,FA review carried out by North Bristol
OL,16,FNHS Trust in 2022 found that more than
OL,17,F200 patients had been given
OL,18,Funnecessary bowel operations by Mr
OL,19,FDixon.
