OL,5,Csuspended
OL,7,FA Medical Practitioners Tribunal
OL,8,FService (MPTS) panel, looking at the
OL,9,Fcare received by five patients, ruled
OL,10,Fhe had made inappropriate comments
OL,11,Fduring consultations.
OL,13,FIt also deemed that Mr Dixon failed to
OL,14,Fadequately outline treatment options
OL,15,Fin a consultation with one patient and
OL,16,Fthat a choice of no treatment was not
OL,17,Fdiscussed.
