OL,7,FAnother woman, known as Patient G,
OL,8,Funderwent a procedure that was not
OL,9,Fclinically indicated and he did not
OL,10,Frecord obtaining her informed consent
OL,11,Ffor the operation.
OL,13,FThe panel heard Mr Dixon's fitness to
OL,14,Fpractise is impaired by reason of
OL,15,Fmisconduct and he was suspended for
OL,16,Fsix months.
