OL,7,FFollowing the conclusion of the
OL,8,Fhearing, Mr Dixon released a lengthy
OL,9,Fstatement apologising to his patients
OL,10,Fand promising to better himself in the
OL,11,Ffuture.
OL,13,FHe said: "I have accepted the findings
OL,14,Fof misconduct made against me by the
OL,15,FMedical Practitioners Tribunal and I
OL,16,Fwill use the six-month period
OL,17,Fsuspension of my medical registration
OL,18,Fto reflect on them.
OL,26,@uD@JOU
