OL,7,F"I would like to start by
OL,8,Facknowledging how difficult it must
OL,9,Fhave been for these former patients of
OL,10,Fmine to come forward and go through
OL,11,Fwhat will have been for them a
OL,12,Fdifficult seven-year process dealing
OL,13,Fwith matters going back almost 13-and-
OL,14,Fa-half years.
OL,16,F"Hearing about their suffering was
OL,17,Fvery difficult and, as the tribunal
OL,18,Fnoted, has had a salutary effect on me.
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@AOU
