OL,3,CSurgeon who carried out hundreds of
OL,4,C'unnecessary' mesh operations is
OL,5,Csuspended
OL,7,F"I hope that they will accept that,
OL,8,Fdespite my wrongdoing, my only wish
OL,9,Fwas to make them better.
OL,11,F"I considered that I was acting in my
OL,12,Fpatients' best interests, as the
OL,13,Ftribunal have accepted.
OL,15,F"I have only ever wanted to seek to
OL,16,Fachieve the best outcome with my
OL,17,Foperations.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUwD@AOU
