OL,4,C'unnecessary' mesh operations is
OL,5,Csuspended
OL,7,F"I am very sorry and deeply regret the
OL,8,Fmisconduct described by the tribunal
OL,9,Fand the consequences they have had on
OL,10,Feveryone.
OL,12,F"I understand that an apology alone
OL,13,Fdoes not begin to diminish the harm
OL,14,Fcaused, but I am committed to learning
OL,15,Ffrom my mistakes and to maintaining
OL,16,Fgenuine changes.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOU
