OL,7,F"It is my utmost priority to regain
OL,8,Fpeople's trust and to continue working
OL,9,Ftowards becoming once again the
OL,10,Fethical and trustworthy doctor that
OL,11,Fevery patient deserves and one that I
OL,12,Fwas previously recognised for.
OL,14,F"The tribunal has accepted the many
OL,15,Fsupportive testimonials received from
OL,16,Fnumerous patients of mine as well as
OL,17,Fmy former colleagues (some of whom `
OL,18,For their family members ` also having
OL,19,Fbeen patients of mine), attesting to
OL,20,Fmy skills as a surgeon, including in
OL,21,Fkeyhole surgery.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
