OL,7,F"I have been honoured by colleagues
OL,8,Fwanting me to perform surgery on them
OL,9,For on their nearest and dearest.
OL,11,F"Going forward, I would like to
OL,12,Fcontinue to prove that I am someone
OL,13,Fwho acts in the best interest of
OL,14,Fpatients in a collaborative way and
OL,15,Fwhom the public can trust ` as I have
OL,16,Fdone for the vast majority of my
OL,17,Fpatients over many years as a surgeon."
