OL,7,FMPTS tribunal chair Emma Boothroyd
OL,8,Fsaid Mr Dixon's failure to obtain
OL,9,Finformed consent from four patients
OL,10,Famounted to "serious misconduct".
OL,12,FShe said: "The psychological impact on
OL,13,Fthese patients was significant and may
OL,14,Fhave exacerbated the physical symptoms
OL,15,Fthey experienced following the
OL,16,Fsurgery."
