OL,7,FLawyers for Mr Dixon had told the
OL,8,Fhearing that the consultant had not
OL,9,Fset out to do anything other than give
OL,10,Fhis best to the patients and he had
OL,11,Frecognised where he went wrong.
OL,13,FTim Whittlestone, Chief Medical
OL,14,FOfficer at North Bristol NHS Trust,
OL,15,Fsaid: "Mr Dixon was dismissed in 2019.
OL,16,FWe have carried out a thorough and
OL,17,Frobust review of affected patients,
OL,18,Fand would like to reiterate our
OL,19,Fapology to all of these individuals.
