OL,12,Fadded: "We apologise to all patients
OL,13,Fwhose care with Mr Dixon fell below
OL,14,Fthe standards that should have been
OL,15,Fprovided at Spire Bristol Hospital.
OL,17,F"We suspended Mr Dixon in 2017, and he
OL,18,Fhas not practised in our hospitals
OL,19,Fsince then. We also referred Mr Dixon
OL,20,Fto the GMC and worked closely with the
OL,21,FGMC in its investigations.
